{"tid":527002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[未來撚阿廢又中?] 侵： 我可能與金正恩發展非常好關係","createTime":"2018-01-12T08:07:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T09:09:07.000Z","uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2bcf1b912d15a3554ed395d93c9b5e010f4726b8","tid":527002,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T08:07:45.000Z","msg":"美國總統川普11日表示，他可能會與北韓領導人金正恩發展出非常好的關係，並表示在推文稱金正恩為「小火箭人」是廣大戰略的一部分。但他拒絕透露是否已經和金正恩接觸過。<br />\n<br />\n川普接受《華爾街日報》專訪時表示，自己並未沒有像外界認為那樣，與金正恩水火不容，「我可能和金正恩之間有非常好的關係」。川普說，他擅長與人建立關係，「我相信你們會對此感到驚訝。」<br />\n<br />\n川普是否曾與金正恩有過接觸？川普表示，他不想評論，「我不是說我有或沒有，我只是不想評論」。<br />\n<br />\n川普與金正恩經常隔空交火，川普曾戲稱金正恩是「火箭人」；金正恩反嗆川普是「老番癲」。但川普最近開始向北韓示好，兩韓會談前，川普表示願意與北韓領導人金正恩通電；兩韓會談後，川普再表示在情況合適下與北韓對話持開放立場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180112001736-260408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20180112001736-260408&d=ZLlp%2BqdNaSGF4Tu9lAAn4UbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=b5df7226\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180112001736-260408</a>"},{"pid":"c5b0ca1ba5cd4a2db2af6b7dc370a6f53774b22d","tid":527002,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T08:10:01.000Z","msg":"ar fai ho ball <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64573a94077538f791084ff72a4e4905b0465bff","tid":527002,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T08:11:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/12/161136_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F12%2F161136_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=db12b512&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef1403e4f226711930bba4af0e18797113852ae7","tid":527002,"uid":148712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T08:30:00.000Z","msg":"打啦，好悶呀"},{"pid":"113fe947f1230116f3fc8a44e63cde